God blessed us with a child.

00:22:25.880 --> 00:22:26.880 align:middle line:-1
A baby girl.

00:22:28.120 --> 00:22:30.840 align:middle line:-2
If I get you married
in another town,

00:22:31.440 --> 00:22:35.080 align:middle line:-2
