and worrying about you.

00:22:36.080 --> 00:22:40.160 align:middle line:-2
Tell me, will I be able to
live if you're far away from me?

00:22:41.000 --> 00:22:42.840 align:middle line:-2
Who said that I'd get married
and live in another town?

00:22:43.080 --> 00:22:45.440 align:middle line:-2
If you study any further,
you will have to go.

00:22:45.880 --> 00:22:48.000 align:middle line:-2
So, I've called them
for your engagement tomorrow.

00:22:48.040 --> 00:22:51.440 align:middle line:-2
Ask them not to come. I want
to study further. Please sign this.

