00:32:02.360 --> 00:32:04.600 align:middle line:-2
Karan! My son!
- Oh, my God!

00:32:04.680 --> 00:32:05.720 align:middle line:-2
Greetings.
- Greetings.

00:32:05.800 --> 00:32:08.360 align:middle line:-1
