University is a friend of mine.

00:33:08.760 --> 00:33:10.000 align:middle line:-1
If you wish,

00:33:10.400 --> 00:33:12.720 align:middle line:-2
I can have a word with him
and have a seat reserved for you.

00:33:13.120 --> 00:33:15.280 align:middle line:-1
Will you go to Mumbai then?

00:33:15.840 --> 00:33:18.160 align:middle line:-2
What difference does it make
