01:45:46.640 --> 01:45:50.040 align:middle line:-1
"You're a performer!"

01:45:50.440 --> 01:45:54.040 align:middle line:-1
"You can't get them to dance!"

01:45:54.240 --> 01:45:59.680 align:middle line:-2
"When it's your turn,
you'll run away!"

01:45:59.760 --> 01:46:01.320 align:middle line:-1
Wow! You're amazing!

01:46:01.400 --> 01:46:03.280 align:middle line:-2
Thanks.
- Amazing!

01:46:03.560 --> 01:46:06.000 align:middle line:-2
Master, that's Altaf Raja's tune.
- What?

01:46:06.120 --> 01:46:08.200 align:middle line:-1
A foreigner?

01:46:08.280 --> 01:46:09.680 align:middle line:-1
He's a famous singer.

01:46:09.760 --> 01:46:12.520 align:middle line:-2
This is a tune from
his famous album.

01:46:13.280 --> 01:46:14.120 align:middle line:-1
How is that possible?

01:46:14.240 --> 01:46:15.840 align:middle line:-2
It is.
- How?

01:46:15.920 --> 01:46:19.560 align:middle line:-2
He must've heard the
tune from you and copied it.

01:46:19.880 --> 01:46:22.160 align:middle line:-1
But this is a three-year old tune.

01:46:22.280 --> 01:46:24.120 align:middle line:-1
What a thief!

01:46:24.560 --> 01:46:29.680 align:middle line:-2
I composed the tune three days ago,
and he stole it three years back!

01:46:29.840 --> 01:46:31.840 align:middle line:-1
No more poetry from today!

01:46:32.000 --> 01:46:35.160 align:middle line:-2
Poonam, what's happening with us?
It's very bad.

01:46:36.160 --> 01:46:39.000 align:middle line:-2
Hi, Pinky.
- Hi, master.

01:46:39.080 --> 01:46:40.960 align:middle line:-2
How are you?
- I'm fine.

01:46:41.000 --> 01:46:43.120 align:middle line:-2
Okay, bye.
- Bye.

01:46:43.200 --> 01:46:44.680 align:middle line:-2
Master.
- Yes?

01:46:44.760 --> 01:46:47.000 align:middle line:-2
How could you tell
that that was Pinky?

01:46:47.040 --> 01:46:49.000 align:middle line:-1
Her perfume gave her away.

01:46:49.040 --> 01:46:52.720 align:middle line:-2
I remember every pretty
lady by her perfume.

01:46:53.400 --> 01:46:54.840 align:middle line:-1
Somebody stinks!

01:46:54.960 --> 01:46:55.960 align:middle line:-1
Get lost.

01:46:59.560 --> 01:47:00.920 align:middle line:-1
Khushi!

01:47:01.000 --> 01:47:02.360 align:middle line:-1
Khushi!

01:47:02.440 --> 01:47:03.680 align:middle line:-2
Poonam,
you like my hair, don't you?

01:47:03.800 --> 01:47:05.080 align:middle line:-2
Yes.
- Here.

01:47:07.200 --> 01:47:10.440 align:middle line:-1
Come on, Khushi. How are you?

01:47:10.560 --> 01:47:11.600 align:middle line:-1
Hi, master.

01:47:11.720 --> 01:47:14.560 align:middle line:-1
What a maintained size!

01:47:14.640 --> 01:47:18.320 align:middle line:-2
Remember, the cultural programme
at the college is fast approaching?

01:47:18.400 --> 01:47:19.680 align:middle line:-1
What about the practise?

01:47:19.760 --> 01:47:22.880 align:middle line:-2
Join Karan immediately
and start your rehearsals.

01:47:22.960 --> 01:47:24.960 align:middle line:-2
Composition, movements... Why?
- No, Master.

01:47:25.840 --> 01:47:27.160 align:middle line:-2
I can't participate
in this function.

01:47:27.240 --> 01:47:28.920 align:middle line:-1
Why not?

01:47:29.360 --> 01:47:31.280 align:middle line:-2
I've told you.
I'm not participating.

01:47:31.720 --> 01:47:35.800 align:middle line:-2
Okay. Bad luck for you.
Better luck next time.

01:47:37.120 --> 01:47:38.960 align:middle line:-2
Mukesh!
- Yes, master.

01:47:39.600 --> 01:47:43.000 align:middle line:-2
Mukesh, make a team of Karan and
Roma and send them on the stage.

01:47:43.080 --> 01:47:45.760 align:middle line:-2
You have my blessings!
- Okay, master.

01:47:45.840 --> 01:47:47.720 align:middle line:-1
I don't want to waste my time.

01:47:48.200 --> 01:47:49.080 align:middle line:-1
Master.

01:47:49.200 --> 01:47:50.960 align:middle line:-1
What again?

01:47:52.120 --> 01:47:53.280 align:middle line:-1
Who's Roma?

01:47:53.880 --> 01:47:56.160 align:middle line:-1
You don't know Roma! Roma!

01:47:56.240 --> 01:47:58.520 align:middle line:-1
A new student in the first year!

01:47:58.640 --> 01:48:00.240 align:middle line:-2
She's kicked up a
storm in the college.

01:48:00.320 --> 01:48:02.520 align:middle line:-2
The students are
crazy about her and

01:48:02.640 --> 01:48:05.720 align:middle line:-2
go around her like blind men.
- What for?

01:48:25.880 --> 01:48:29.080 align:middle line:-2
Excuse me!
- Yes.

01:48:29.160 --> 01:48:31.560 align:middle line:-1
Could you help me cross the road?

01:48:32.120 --> 01:48:33.120 align:middle line:-1
Sure.

01:48:41.320 --> 01:48:44.920 align:middle line:-2
You've crossed the road.
- Small road.

01:48:45.000 --> 01:48:48.240 align:middle line:-2
What?
- You've helped a blind man.

01:48:48.320 --> 01:48:51.240 align:middle line:-2
Thank you so much.
You are large-hearted.

01:48:51.600 --> 01:48:53.280 align:middle line:-2
It's okay.
- Okay.

01:48:54.840 --> 01:48:56.560 align:middle line:-1
Darn! I missed it.

01:49:03.200 --> 01:49:04.120 align:middle line:-1
Karan.

01:49:08.360 --> 01:49:09.240 align:middle line:-1
What is the matter?

01:49:09.320 --> 01:49:10.360 align:middle line:-1
Priya has sent a letter.

01:49:11.280 --> 01:49:12.280 align:middle line:-1
You can give it to Vicky.

01:49:12.360 --> 01:49:13.360 align:middle line:-1
It's not for him.

01:49:13.440 --> 01:49:14.720 align:middle line:-2
Is it for me?
- No.

01:49:14.840 --> 01:49:16.240 align:middle line:-2
It must be for you then.
- Not.

01:49:16.320 --> 01:49:18.920 align:middle line:-2
If not for me, you nor Vicky...
- It's for the two of us!

01:49:25.120 --> 01:49:27.200 align:middle line:-1
To Karan and Khushi.

01:49:30.320 --> 01:49:31.440 align:middle line:-1
You read it.

01:49:37.760 --> 01:49:39.200 align:middle line:-1
Dear Karan and Khushi.

01:49:41.200 --> 01:49:43.280 align:middle line:-1
I love Vicky so dearly,

01:49:43.720 --> 01:49:46.240 align:middle line:-2
I don't think anyone in
the world loves anyone as much.

01:49:47.160 --> 01:49:51.840 align:middle line:-2
You must think why every
lover in the world says that.

01:49:52.600 --> 01:49:54.960 align:middle line:-2
It's because they have
true love for each other.

01:49:55.640 --> 01:49:59.400 align:middle line:-2
And the suffering of separation
those truly in love go through,

01:49:59.880 --> 01:50:01.360 align:middle line:-1
only I know about.

01:50:01.960 --> 01:50:07.080 align:middle line:-2
I'm pining to meet Vicky.
Please bring us together.

01:50:08.680 --> 01:50:09.800 align:middle line:-1
Yours, Priya.

01:50:11.560 --> 01:50:12.680 align:middle line:-1
What are we to do now?

01:50:15.360 --> 01:50:17.360 align:middle line:-2
Priya has a friend
called Shehnaz, right?

01:50:18.760 --> 01:50:20.040 align:middle line:-1
Isn't this pretty?

01:50:20.240 --> 01:50:21.120 align:middle line:-1
Did you like it?

01:50:22.040 --> 01:50:23.080 align:middle line:-1
Hello, uncle.

01:50:23.880 --> 01:50:26.000 align:middle line:-2
How are you, Rukhsana?
- I am Fine!

01:50:26.760 --> 01:50:28.000 align:middle line:-1
Be careful, Vicky.

01:50:28.120 --> 01:50:29.880 align:middle line:-2
Be careful.
I'll take care. Don't worry.

01:50:32.280 --> 01:50:34.440 align:middle line:-2
The two of you chat,
I'm going to bed.

01:50:42.240 --> 01:50:43.360 align:middle line:-2
Priya!
- Yes.

01:50:43.960 --> 01:50:45.080 align:middle line:-1
Who's this girl?

01:50:45.720 --> 01:50:48.120 align:middle line:-1
It's Shabana. Shehnaz's friend.

01:50:56.840 --> 01:51:00.880 align:middle line:-2
Is she coming here
for the first time?

01:51:02.000 --> 01:51:02.960 align:middle line:-1
Yes.

01:51:03.000 --> 01:51:08.320 align:middle line:-2
I see. Go ahead and
chat with Rukhsana,

01:51:09.000 --> 01:51:11.240 align:middle line:-1
I'll take Shabana around the house.

01:51:11.320 --> 01:51:13.200 align:middle line:-2
Come on, Shabana.
- Run away, Vicky!

01:51:15.000 --> 01:51:16.080 align:middle line:-1
Wait!

01:51:23.000 --> 01:51:24.440 align:middle line:-1
Get in, Vicky!

01:51:24.560 --> 01:51:25.800 align:middle line:-1
Let's go.

01:51:28.640 --> 01:51:32.320 align:middle line:-1
MH-01-B-906.

01:51:40.680 --> 01:51:43.200 align:middle line:-1
Car number 906. Is it yours?

01:51:44.440 --> 01:51:45.880 align:middle line:-2
Yes.
- Karan?

01:51:46.040 --> 01:51:47.120 align:middle line:-1
Yes.

01:51:47.520 --> 01:51:48.600 align:middle line:-1
Karan.

01:53:12.000 --> 01:53:13.200 align:middle line:-1
Karan!

01:53:13.280 --> 01:53:14.640 align:middle line:-1
Karan!

01:53:50.320 --> 01:53:51.320 align:middle line:-1
Khushi!

01:53:52.320 --> 01:53:53.320 align:middle line:-1
Khushi.

01:54:25.160 --> 01:54:26.440 align:middle line:-1
Let me do it.

01:55:17.200 --> 01:55:18.560 align:middle line:-1
Good morning.

01:55:18.680 --> 01:55:20.600 align:middle line:-2
Hey man, who are you?
- Me?

01:55:20.760 --> 01:55:22.520 align:middle line:-1
How are you related to the girl?

01:55:23.000 --> 01:55:23.880 align:middle line:-1
I...

01:55:24.160 --> 01:55:27.240 align:middle line:-2
Whoever you are,
help me with the injection.

01:55:27.600 --> 01:55:28.440 align:middle line:-1
All right.

01:55:29.920 --> 01:55:30.800 align:middle line:-1
Injection?

01:55:40.240 --> 01:55:42.680 align:middle line:-1
In the waist.

01:55:42.800 --> 01:55:43.640 align:middle line:-1
Alright.

01:55:45.000 --> 01:55:46.360 align:middle line:-2
No!
- What?

01:55:46.440 --> 01:55:47.680 align:middle line:-1
Give it to her in the arm.

01:55:47.800 --> 01:55:50.000 align:middle line:-1
This is meant for the waist.

01:55:50.040 --> 01:55:51.520 align:middle line:-1
No, give it to her in the arm.

01:55:51.600 --> 01:55:53.720 align:middle line:-2
The one for the arm
is given on the arm,

01:55:53.840 --> 01:55:55.840 align:middle line:-2
the one for the waist
is given on the waist.

01:55:55.920 --> 01:55:58.320 align:middle line:-1
Doctor!

01:55:58.840 --> 01:56:02.000 align:middle line:-2
You don't know anything
about this waist, doctor.

01:56:02.160 --> 01:56:06.840 align:middle line:-2
Doctor, this waist has caused
a big problem already.

01:56:07.000 --> 01:56:10.840 align:middle line:-2
If I go into details,
it'll take at least 2 hours.

01:56:10.920 --> 01:56:13.680 align:middle line:-2
Your duty hours will be over
and when the next doctor come sin,

01:56:13.800 --> 01:56:17.520 align:middle line:-2
I'll have to explain to him!
Have mercy on me,

01:56:17.600 --> 01:56:20.240 align:middle line:-1
and give it to her in the arm.

01:56:20.320 --> 01:56:21.600 align:middle line:-1
Nurse, send him out.

01:56:21.760 --> 01:56:24.680 align:middle line:-1
That's all right!

01:56:24.760 --> 01:56:29.080 align:middle line:-2
I mean, you can give
it wherever you wish.

01:56:29.240 --> 01:56:33.080 align:middle line:-2
Give it to anyone.
To her, the nurse or yourself,

01:56:33.320 --> 01:56:35.640 align:middle line:-2
I've seen nothing.
I will see nothing!

01:56:37.160 --> 01:56:41.080 align:middle line:-2
God, why did You
make this waist? Why?

01:57:06.200 --> 01:57:09.880 align:middle line:-1
"I've given you..."

01:57:11.560 --> 01:57:14.680 align:middle line:-1
"My heart"

01:57:15.320 --> 01:57:24.240 align:middle line:-1
"My love, what have you done?"

01:57:24.320 --> 01:57:29.000 align:middle line:-1
"When I saw you,"

01:57:29.080 --> 01:57:33.640 align:middle line:-2
"I realised that I'm
crazy about you."

01:57:33.760 --> 01:57:38.520 align:middle line:-1
"It's something my heart knows."

01:57:38.600 --> 01:57:43.440 align:middle line:-2
"You're the one I've
taken to be my beloved."

01:57:48.720 --> 01:57:57.000 align:middle line:-1
"I've given you my heart."

01:57:57.760 --> 01:58:02.960 align:middle line:-1
"My love..."

01:58:03.320 --> 01:58:06.440 align:middle line:-1
"What have you done?"

01:58:51.840 --> 01:58:56.000 align:middle line:-2
"On your lips is a smile.
Your eyes hold intoxication."

01:58:56.080 --> 01:59:00.160 align:middle line:-2
"The sight of you
makes my heart sway."

01:59:00.640 --> 01:59:02.960 align:middle line:-1
"I love you all day and night."

01:59:03.000 --> 01:59:05.880 align:middle line:-2
"I find peace only
after meeting you."

01:59:05.960 --> 01:59:14.240 align:middle line:-2
"Your dark tresses lend
a fragrance to my being."

01:59:14.680 --> 01:59:17.160 align:middle line:-1
"All I wish to say is that"

01:59:17.280 --> 01:59:19.640 align:middle line:-1
"it's your arms I must stay in."

01:59:19.760 --> 01:59:24.240 align:middle line:-1
"Don't ever forget this promise."

01:59:24.440 --> 01:59:29.000 align:middle line:-2
"Don't make me cry,
now that you've made me smile."

01:59:29.240 --> 01:59:33.720 align:middle line:-1
"Don't make excuses."

01:59:34.000 --> 01:59:38.280 align:middle line:-1
"Don't ever hide anything from me."

01:59:44.520 --> 01:59:52.360 align:middle line:-1
"I've given you my heart."

02:00:40.200 --> 02:00:48.000 align:middle line:-2
"My dream, my desire, is to adorn
your arms with bridal bangles."

02:00:48.920 --> 02:00:53.800 align:middle line:-2
"These lovely meetings,
I love your talk."

02:00:53.880 --> 02:00:56.040 align:middle line:-1
"If you agree,

02:00:56.160 --> 02:01:02.760 align:middle line:-2
"I'd bring the bridal
palanquin to your house."

02:01:03.200 --> 02:01:08.000 align:middle line:-2
"I spend my nights pining.
I dream of marriage."

02:01:08.160 --> 02:01:12.760 align:middle line:-2
"You must embellish
my world of love."

02:01:12.960 --> 02:01:16.920 align:middle line:-1
"Never leave me."

02:01:17.640 --> 02:01:21.920 align:middle line:-1
"Keep your promises."

02:01:22.360 --> 02:01:26.440 align:middle line:-1
"Hold me in your arms."

02:01:32.680 --> 02:01:41.040 align:middle line:-1
"I've given you my heart."

02:01:41.560 --> 02:01:46.280 align:middle line:-1
"My love..."

02:01:47.160 --> 02:01:49.960 align:middle line:-1
"What have you done?"

02:02:03.560 --> 02:02:04.920 align:middle line:-1
What is it? What?

02:02:05.520 --> 02:02:07.800 align:middle line:-2
I tried several times
to meet you at your office,

02:02:07.960 --> 02:02:10.560 align:middle line:-2
but you staff
wouldn't let me. So...

02:02:12.400 --> 02:02:13.600 align:middle line:-1
My name is Karan.

02:02:15.240 --> 02:02:18.800 align:middle line:-2
Vicky's my friend, sir.
He has no past to tell you about.

02:02:19.240 --> 02:02:22.360 align:middle line:-2
At present, he's a student
but he has a very bright future.

02:02:22.520 --> 02:02:24.320 align:middle line:-1
You don't know that, but I do.

02:02:24.920 --> 02:02:27.840 align:middle line:-2
At my age, my father was
even worse off than Vicky is.

02:02:29.000 --> 02:02:32.200 align:middle line:-2
At this age, even you...
Please don't feel bad.

02:02:32.720 --> 02:02:34.200 align:middle line:-1
You used to be a small-time thug.

02:02:36.040 --> 02:02:37.200 align:middle line:-1
But I tell you, at your age,

02:02:37.320 --> 02:02:41.880 align:middle line:-2
Vicky will be far ahead of you,
even my father and me.

02:02:43.760 --> 02:02:46.360 align:middle line:-2
Apart from all this,
he has a very kind heart.

02:02:49.360 --> 02:02:51.360 align:middle line:-2
When a boy falls
in love with a girl,

02:02:53.280 --> 02:02:55.880 align:middle line:-2
and he finds the girl
without any problem,

02:02:57.920 --> 02:02:59.600 align:middle line:-1
imagine how happy it'll make him.

02:03:01.320 --> 02:03:02.960 align:middle line:-1
Please don't separate them.

02:03:03.320 --> 02:03:04.680 align:middle line:-1
Please unite them.

02:03:04.880 --> 02:03:06.000 align:middle line:-1
Please.

02:03:13.360 --> 02:03:16.160 align:middle line:-2
Your two minutes are up.
Let's go, Goty.

02:03:19.840 --> 02:03:21.320 align:middle line:-1
Did he have nothing to say?

02:03:22.200 --> 02:03:25.200 align:middle line:-2
Your two minutes are up, he said.
And left.

02:03:25.360 --> 02:03:26.600 align:middle line:-1
Oh!

02:03:28.920 --> 02:03:31.240 align:middle line:-1
All right. Even if he said nothing,

02:03:32.000 --> 02:03:35.160 align:middle line:-2
couldn't you guess
what was on his mind?

02:03:35.360 --> 02:03:36.200 align:middle line:-1
What?

02:03:37.960 --> 02:03:41.600 align:middle line:-2
Couldn't you guess
what was on his mind?

02:03:43.920 --> 02:03:45.920 align:middle line:-2
If one knew what's
on everyone's mind,

02:03:46.160 --> 02:03:47.240 align:middle line:-2
there wouldn't be
any problem at all.

02:03:47.680 --> 02:03:49.960 align:middle line:-2
We have these problems
because we don't know.

02:03:50.000 --> 02:03:51.080 align:middle line:-1
What do you mean by these problems?

02:03:51.400 --> 02:03:52.960 align:middle line:-1
These problems. Period.

02:03:56.720 --> 02:03:59.160 align:middle line:-1
All right. I must leave now.

02:03:59.920 --> 02:04:00.840 align:middle line:-1
Bye.

02:04:01.360 --> 02:04:02.520 align:middle line:-1
Khushi.

02:04:13.240 --> 02:04:14.280 align:middle line:-1
Did you call?

02:04:16.640 --> 02:04:17.720 align:middle line:-1
Yes.

02:04:17.880 --> 02:04:18.960 align:middle line:-1
What for?

02:04:19.920 --> 02:04:22.200 align:middle line:-1
To talk.

02:04:22.280 --> 02:04:24.240 align:middle line:-1
That's what we've been doing.

02:04:25.800 --> 02:04:28.080 align:middle line:-2
No, there's something
else I want to talk about.

02:04:33.920 --> 02:04:34.880 align:middle line:-1
What is it about?

02:04:38.000 --> 02:04:43.440 align:middle line:-2
She knows why!
Must she ask what it's about?

02:04:44.080 --> 02:04:45.640 align:middle line:-1
The arrogant one!

02:04:47.080 --> 02:04:48.240 align:middle line:-1
Okay.

02:04:50.080 --> 02:04:53.120 align:middle line:-1
It's about what you are thinking.

02:04:55.640 --> 02:04:58.960 align:middle line:-2
I'm thinking about nothing.
You wanted to talk to me.

02:04:59.040 --> 02:05:00.280 align:middle line:-1
So tell me what you want to.

02:05:11.400 --> 02:05:12.960 align:middle line:-2
Bye.
- What?

02:05:15.040 --> 02:05:16.560 align:middle line:-1
Bye.

02:05:19.800 --> 02:05:21.320 align:middle line:-1
Is that what you called me to say?

02:05:22.040 --> 02:05:22.960 align:middle line:-1
Yes.

02:05:26.600 --> 02:05:29.040 align:middle line:-1
Okay, bye.

02:06:26.840 --> 02:06:29.080 align:middle line:-2
Karan, I need you.
- What?

02:06:29.600 --> 02:06:31.400 align:middle line:-2
I love you.
- What?

02:06:31.600 --> 02:06:32.720 align:middle line:-1
You know...

02:06:33.240 --> 02:06:36.040 align:middle line:-1
Your intoxicating eyes,

02:06:38.360 --> 02:06:41.360 align:middle line:-1
your lips.

02:06:44.840 --> 02:06:46.080 align:middle line:-1
Oh!

02:06:46.360 --> 02:06:49.440 align:middle line:-1
There's a huge list I have of you.

02:06:53.240 --> 02:06:55.840 align:middle line:-1
Okay.

